
Please download RepLab 2013 dataset from http://nlp.uned.es/replab2013

Note that content of the tweets is not included in the dataset.
Tweets can be downloaded by using the twitter-tools used to obtain the TREC Tweets2011 Collection: https://github.com/lintool/twitter-tools/wiki/Tweets2011-Collection

This software expects the following data:

- The TSV files containing the content of the tweets for each entity in both training and test sets:
   corpus/training/tweet_text/RL2013D01E001.tsv 
   ...
   
   corpus/test/tweet_text/RL2013D01E001.tsv 
   ...
   


- Goldstandard for the RepLab 2013 Filtering Task:

goldstandard/training/goldstandard_filtering.dat
goldstandard/test/goldstandard_fitering.dat

